    <item>
      <title>七国集团盟国警告伊朗不要向俄罗斯供应导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/g-7-allies-warn-iran-against-supplying-russia-with-missiles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[七国集团警告伊朗不要向俄罗斯提供弹道导弹用于乌克兰战争，并威胁称如果伊朗这样做，伊朗将迅速做出反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/g-7-allies-warn-iran-against-supplying-russia-with-missiles</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 15:15:06 GMT</pubDate>
